SubjectFinal Acts of the World Radiocommunication Conference of the International Telecommunication Union
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to bring into force for Canada the FINAL ACTS OF THE WORLD RADIOCOMMUNICATION CONFERENCE OF THE INTERNATIONAL TELECOMMUNICATION UNION, done at Geneva on 27 November 2015.
